'''Carbanti United Electronics''',<ref name="Low Red Moon">''[[Star Wars Outlaws: Low Red Moon]]''</ref> or simply '''Carbanti''', was the producer of Carbanti transceiver packages, the main setup for a [[T-65B X-wing starfighter|T-65B X-wing]] [[starfighter]]'s [[sensor]] system. The Carbanti transceiver package was comprised of a [[Fabritech]] [[ANs-5d "lock track" full-spectrum transceiver]], a [[Melihat]] [["Multi Imager" dedicated energy receptor]], and a [[Tana Ire]] [[Electro-photo receptor]].<ref name="SWCT" />

